   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Sarapion, the strategos, and Serenus, the royal secretary, of the division of Herakleides of the Arsinoite nome, and to the village secretary of Perseai, from Harpokration, son of Herakle( ), of the metropolis. I declare the 5 5/8 arourai of catoecic land belonging to me near the village of Perseai, entered for taxation in the name of Souchas, son of Mysthes, as unwatered for the present 10th year. Wherefore I present this declaration.;(2nd hand) I, Phaseis, village secretary, have received a copy for verification. Phamenoth 1.;;Verso;;(1st hand) Catoecic land of Perseai.;(3rd hand) . . . to Sarapion, strategos of the Arsinoite nome.</ab>
         </div>
